*Igraš* se sa svojim prijateljima u parku. (You play with your friends in the park.)

*Igraš* tenis svakog vikenda. (You play tennis every weekend.)

*Igraš* na gitaru. (You play the guitar.)

*Igraš* se sa svojim psom. (You play with your dog.)

Ona *igra* klavir. (She plays the piano.)

*Igra* se u školi. (They play at school.)

Oni danas *igraju* fudbal. (They are playing football today.)

*Igraju* se u dvorištu. (They are playing in the yard.)

*Igraju* se sa loptom. (They are playing with a ball.)

Mi *igramo* video igre. (We are playing video games.)